newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,278 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,278 contracts.

text.p: its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 1,278 contracts verjsus 751 overnight Thursday.
There were 109 wheat, 398 corn, 700 soybean, 18 soymeal, 30 soyoil, 11 oat, three corn call, six corn put, two soybean call and one soybean put contracts traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was steady to 3/4 cent higher, corn was unchanged to 1/4 cent higher and soybeans were 1/4 cent lower to 5-1/4 cents higher.
